name: LG G5 H860 32GB - Gold
description:
All New Metal Design Beauty in the palm of your hands. Metal and glass smoothly float together uninterrupted, without an antenna slit. The sleek design of iconic simplicity comes in a variety of rich colors. Unparalleled comfort and fit, that you must hold to believe. Modular Type Break Free. The changeable module with slide-out battery unleashes a world of unlimited options. 

Wide Angle Lens Get the whole picture! Our eyes can take in a lot, but this camera grabs even more at 135°. Capture a sprawling skyline, a packed stadium concert, or the entire beach, all that your eyes can see plus more. Magnifying Zoom In and Out Go Extreme! Zoom out ultra wide (0.5X) for the first time ever on a smartphone. Take a variety of photos and videos from a tight close-up to a vast scene by simply pinching the screen. Just pinch to see it all. Pop-out Picture The photo is the frame. Take both a standard and wide angle photo at the same time. Make your picture pop and stand out against 4 photo-frame background effects: Fisheye, B&W, Vignette and Lens blur. Your uploads will always get the thumbs-up & hearts of your followers! 

Daylight Mode A different kind of "Sun" screen. When the sun shines bright, so does the screen. The enhanced IPS Quantum display is brighter, more vivid, and clearer even in outdoor day light. Always-on Display Save your thumbs. No more hitting the button to check the time, date, or notifications. With the LG G5, the important stuff is already up and on! Just look. LG Friends Manager All together now. With the LG G5's Friends Manager app on, you can connect, interact and play with all your LG friends.

Feature

- Qualcomm Snapdragon MSM8996 Quad Core 2.1GHz

- 4GB RAM, 32GB Internal Storage

- 5.3" (1440 x 2560) QHD IPS Display

- 16 MP Main Camera (F1.8 Normal 78°) with OIS 2.0

- 8 MP Front Camera

- Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac

- Bluetooth v4.2 BLE

- USB Type-C Port

- Android Marshmallow 6.0

Specification

description:
Nexus 5 is the upcoming successor to Google's super-hit smartphone Nexus 4. It is being developed in cooperation with Korean tech giant LG which also co-manufactured the Nexus 4 for Google. Although, the smartphone has not been announced officially by the two manufacturers, a lot of specs have been leaked on the internet and give a glimpse of what, potentially, could be actual Nexus 5 features.

The smartphone is expected to come pre-loaded with Android OS v4.4 (KitKat). Some images leaked suggest an improved Android UI and brand new wallpaper as well. It is rumored that the phone will come with a True HD IPS touchscreen that's 5.0-inch in size and offers a pixel density of 441 for breathtaking clarity. It is not clear how thin the device will be, but considering previous Nexus releases, we can expect a sleek and stylish handset with a trademark glossy glass back cover.

Nexus 5 is also rumored to be equipped with a Quad-core processor having a clock rate of 2.3GHz. It will be housed on the latest Snapdragon 800 SoC. The chip will provide a 3GB built-in RAM while an Adreno 330 GPU is expected to power the phone's graphics acceleration. Other specs likely to be offered on the Nexus 5 are Wi-Fi, 4G support, NFC, Bluetooth 4.0, Nano SIM card slot, USB Slim Port, HTML5 browser, 8MP primary HD camera, front cam, GPS and a built-in non-removable battery.

name: LG V10 H961N 64GB Space Black
description:
Always pushing the boundaries of smartphone innovation, the LG V10 features multimedia capabilities never before seen in a mobile device. 

The second screen can be set to display the weather, time, date and battery icon when the main display is off. With the main display on, the Second Screen can be set to convert to a dedicated launch area for shortcuts or your favorite apps. 

The LG V10 features 5MP Dual Front Cameras with two separate lenses to capture standard 80° selfies or perfect wide angle selfies of 120°, without the need to pan the smartphone which increases the likelihood of camera shake. The V10 is the first smartphone to offer manual mode for video. With Manual Video Mode, budding directors can easily create professional-quality videos by adjusting options such as shutter speed, frame rate, ISO, white balance and focus while recording. 

The V10’s frame is composed of SAE grade 316L stainless steel, the same tough, hypoallergenic material used to make surgical tools and high-end watches. On the back of LG V10, resilient but soft Dura Skin offers added protection from direct impacts to the device. 

The V10 features 32 bit Hi-Fi DAC by ESS Technology, designers of high-performance audio products for professionals. The LG V10 automatically detects connected devices and provides sound control options which can be customized. And the LG V10 is the first commercial device to utilize Qualcomm Technologies TruSignal™ antenna boost technology designed to intelligently optimize signal strength at all times for fewer dropped calls, faster data and better call coverage, no matter how the phone is held.

Along with the popular Knock Code, the LG V10 features a new fingerprint sensor to unlock the smartphone and turn on the display simultaneously.

Feature

- 5.7" (1440 x 2560) QHD IPS Quantum Display

- Second Screen: IPS Quantum Display (160 x 1040)

- 1.8GHz Qualcomm Snapdragon 808 Hexa-Core Processor

- 64GB ROM / 4GB RAM

- 16 MP Primary Camera (F1.8 with OIS 2.0)

- 5 MP Dual Front Camera (F2.2 Wide 120°, F2.0 Normal 80°) 

- Manual Video Mode

- Fingerprint ID

- 3000 mAh Removable (Li-Ion) Battery

- Android™ 5.1.1 (Lollipop)

name: LG V10 H961N Dual Sim 64GB - Space Black
description:
Natural design of a premium smartphone has arrived. Integrated with Dura Skin, the shiny stainless steel 316L frame, commonly used in luxury watches for years, provides a unique look and superior protection against dings and breaks. The amazing true-to-life images and authentic rich colors produced by the IPS Quantum Display highlights the final touch to this master piece. The LG V10 brings an unmatched experience and visual satisfaction.

Whether the main screen is on or off, the second screen keeps you up-to-date. When the main screen is off, it becomes your 24/7 billboard for basic information such as weather, date, time, and battery life, or for your personal signature to authenticate ownership. Swiping it allows immediate access to Quick Tools, an easy shortcut panel to Silent Mode, Wi-Fi, flash, and camera. When you turn on the main screen, it becomes a multitasking panel to quickly switch between recent apps, favorite contacts, music player and upcoming events.

Be adventurous and start recording while on the move. With the existing OIS camera and the new image processor, the LG V10 records images with more fluid motions allowing videos playback without motion blurs. Create professional videos without the shakes. Direct stories like an auteur and shoot like a pro. With Manual Video Mode, you can bring your imagination to life through film. Now you can master film in real time and do cool functions like color correction and manage picture quality. Be the cinematographer of your life and capture only your best memories.

- 5.7" (1440 x 2560) QHD IPS Quantum Display

All repairs are carried out by the manufacturers authorised repair agents any where in the world including Australia. In the event that this equipment requires any repair or service you must visit www.mackcam.com and arrange for service to obtain a Repair Authorisation Number.

Diamond warranty service starts from date of invoice.

The Digital Still, Video or Lens equipment covered by this service contract is guaranteed to operate according to manufacturer’s specifications for a period of 3 years from the date of purchase. Mack Camera & Video Service, Inc. shall repair, service or replace same to operate properly.

This Mack Camera & Video Service Inc. service contract covers:
* Manufacturer Defects
* Impact Damage
* Sand/Grit Damage
* Accidental and Unintentional Abuse
* Mechanical Malfunctions
* Normal and Abnormal Wear and Tear

How to Register

name: Microsoft Lumia 950XL 4G 32GB Unlocked Mobile - Black (with keyboard)
description:
Stay connected and productive with the Microsoft Lumia 950 XL 32GB Smartphone. This smartphone features a 5.7" 2560 x 1440 qHD AMOLED display delivering a pixel density of 518 ppi. Under the hood, a Snapdragon 810 CPU with an octa-core processor running up to 2 GHz, an Adreno 430 GPU, and 3GB of RAM keep its Windows 10 operating system running smoothly. 

This device features Continuum, which lets you use your smartphone like a PC, and Hello Beta, which quickly unlocks your phone by recognizing your face with infrared sensors. It also has a 20MP rear camera with Carl Zeiss optics that can capture 4K video as well as a 5MP front-facing camera. 

The Lumia 950 XL connects to 4G LTE wireless networks or to 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac Wi-Fi. 32GB of internal storage is complemented by a microSD slot that accommodates cards up to 200GB. The phone charges and transfers data via its USB-C port, which can charge the phone from 10% to 50% in 30 minutes. Alternatively, integrated Qi wireless charging lets you power up by simply placing the phone on a Qi charging pad. The 3340mAh battery is removable and offers up to 25 hours of talk time and up to 12 days on standby. A USB-C cable and charger are included.

Get full-sized keyboard functionality for your compatible mobile device with the Universal Foldable Bluetooth Keyboard from Microsoft. This compact, portable keyboard is designed to work with most Bluetooth-enabled devices, including iPad, iPhone, Android, and Windows tablets and smartphones. It's equipped with Bluetooth Smart technology, so you won't have to hassle with any extra cables or wires. Additionally, this keyboard can simultaneously pair with up to two devices, enabling you to switch between projects or platforms with a single touch. Its built-in rechargeable battery lasts up to 3 months on a single full charge.

 

Feature

- GSM / 4G LTE Capable

- International Variant/US Compatible LTE

- 20MP 1/2.4" Camera Sensor

- 26mm f/1.9 Zeiss Lens with OIS

- 2 GHz Snapdragon 810 Octacore CPU

- 32GB Storage Capacity + 3GB of RAM

- 5.7" qHD 2560 x 1440 AMOLED Display

- microSD Expandable up to 200GB

- Windows 10 with Continuum Support

- With Keyboard

Specification

name: Microsoft Lumia 950XL Dual sim 3GB RAM 32GB ROM - White
description:
Stay connected and productive with the Microsoft Lumia 950 XL 32GB Dual-SIM Smartphone. This smartphone features a 5.7" 2560 x 1440 qHD AMOLED display delivering a pixel density of 518 ppi. Under the hood, a Snapdragon 810 CPU with an octa-core processor running up to 2 GHz, an Adreno 430 GPU, and 3GB of RAM keep its Windows 10 operating system running smoothly. 

This device features Continuum, which lets you use your smartphone like a PC, and Hello Beta, which quickly unlocks your phone by recognizing your face with infrared sensors. It also has a 20MP rear camera with Carl Zeiss optics that can capture 4K video as well as a 5MP front-facing camera. 

The Lumia 950 XL connects to 4G LTE wireless networks or to 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac Wi-Fi. 32GB of internal storage is complemented by a microSD slot that accommodates cards up to 200GB. The phone charges and transfers data via its USB-C port, which can charge the phone from 10% to 50% in 30 minutes. Alternatively, integrated Qi wireless charging lets you power up by simply placing the phone on a Qi charging pad. The 3340mAh battery is removable and offers up to 25 hours of talk time and up to 12 days on standby. A USB-C cable and charger are included.

description:
The silver Microsoft 13.5" Surface Book Multi-Touch 2-in-1 Notebook is a high-performance laptop/tablet hybrid with power and versatility. The Surface Book packs an Intel 6th gen (Skylake) dual-core processor into a magnesium casing with a silver finish. Use the tactile keyboard and touchpad to stay productive. You can also detach the screen from the dock and use the Surface Book as a tablet. The included Surface Pen provides added precision thanks to its 1024 levels of pressure sensitivity.

With a 13.5" PixelSense display, the Surface Book features a 3000 x 2000 screen resolution (267 ppi) and a 3:2 aspect ratio. The display is also a 10-point touch support so you can take full advantage of the multi-touch gestures incorporated into Windows 10 Pro. If you want to output video to an external display, you can use the mini DisplayPort.

The system is powered by a dual-core 6th generation (Skylake) 2.4 GHz Intel Core i5-6300U processor with integrated Intel HD Graphics 520. It also has 8GB of RAM, a 128GB solid state drive, an SD media card slot, 802.11ac Wi-Fi, Bluetooth 4.0, a 5MP front-facing camera, an 8MP rear-facing camera with autofocus and 1080p HD video recording, and dual integrated microphones. There are also built-in front-facing stereo speakers with Dolby audio. Windows 10 Pro is the installed operating system.

name: Microsoft Surface Pro 4 / Pro 3 Type Cover US Layout - Blue
description:
Fully redesigned, the Surface Pro 4/Pro3 Type Cover is thinner and lighter than before with improved magnetic stability for lap use. It also has a mechanical keyboard with optimal key spacing for fast and fluid typing, plus an enlarged track pad for precision control and navigation.

Surface Pro 4/Pro3 Type Cover has a new improved design with slightly spread out keys for a more familiar and efficient typing experience. The two-button trackpad is now larger for precision control and navigation.

The keyboard is sturdy with enhanced magnetic stability along the fold, so you can adjust it to the right angle and work on your lap, on the plane, or at your desk. Since it’s designed just for Surface, the Surface Pro 4/Pro3 Type Cover easily clicks into place to go from tablet to laptop instantly.

Fold Surface Pro 4/Pro3 Type Cover back like a magazine for a tablet experience with Surface Pro 4/Pro3. The keys are disabled when the cover is flipped back to avoid inadvertent typing. When you close Surface Pro 4/Pro3 Type Cover over the display, it functions as a protective shell, shielding the screen from bumps and scratches. 

Surface Pro 4/Pro3 Type Cover is made from premium materials and feels soft to the touch yet sturdy and quieter when typing. It’s available in multiple colors so you can express your personal style. Plus Surface Pro 4/Pro3 Type Cover is backlit, so you can continue working after the lights go out.

Feature

- Support Surface Pro 4/Pro 3

- 295mm x 216mm x 4.65mm

- 292g weight

- Activation: Moving (mechanical) keys

- Layout: QWERTY, full row of function keys (F1 – F12)

- Dedicated buttons for Windows shortcuts, media controls, screen brightness

- Right click button

- Magnetic interface

- Accelerometer sensors

Specification

Microsoft Surface Pro 4 / Pro 3 Type Cover US Layout - Blue

name: Microsoft Surface Pro 4 i5 128GB 4GB RAM [without Keyboard]
description:
Microsoft combines the portability of a tablet and the performance of a laptop with the 12.3" Surface Pro 4 128GB Multi-Touch Tablet. Weighing just 1.73 pounds and measuring just 0.33" thin, the Surface Pro 4 packs an Intel 6th gen (Skylake) dual-core processor into a magnesium casing with a silver finish. Use the multi-position Kickstand and the Surface Pro 4 Type Cover (sold separately) to turn the Surface Pro 4 into a laptop. The included Surface Pen provides up to 1024 levels of pressure sensitivity.

The Surface Pro 4 features a 12.3" PixelSense display with a 2736 x 1824 screen resolution (267 ppi) and a 3:2 aspect ratio. The display is also a 10-point touch support so you can take full advantage of the multi-touch gestures incorporated into Windows 10 Pro. If you want to output video to an external display, you can use the mini DisplayPort.

The system is powered by a dual-core 6th generation (Skylake) Intel Core i5 processor with Intel HD Graphics 520. It also has 4GB of RAM, a 128GB solid state drive, a microSD media card slot, 802.11a/b/g/n/ac Wi-Fi, Bluetooth 4.0, a 5MP front-facing camera, an 8MP rear-facing camera with 1080p HD video recording, and dual integrated microphones. There are also built-in stereo speakers with Dolby audio. Windows 10 Pro is the installed operating system.

name: Microsoft Surface Pro 4 M3 128GB 4GB RAM [without Keyboard]
description:
Microsoft combines the portability of a tablet and the performance of a laptop with the 12.3" Surface Pro 4 128GB Multi-Touch Tablet. Weighing just 1.69 pounds and measuring just 0.33" thin, the Surface Pro 4 packs an Intel 6th gen (Skylake) dual-core processor into a magnesium casing with a silver finish. Use the multi-position Kickstand and the Surface Pro 4 Type Cover (sold separately) to turn the Surface Pro 4 into a laptop. The included Surface Pen provides up to 1024 levels of pressure sensitivity.

The Surface Pro 4 features a 12.3" PixelSense display with a 2736 x 1824 screen resolution (267 ppi) and a 3:2 aspect ratio. The display is also a 10-point touch support so you can take full advantage of the multi-touch gestures incorporated into Windows 10 Pro. If you want to output video to an external display, you can use the mini DisplayPort.

The system is powered by a dual-core 6th generation (Skylake) Intel Core m3 processor with Intel HD Graphics 515. It also has 4GB of RAM, a 128GB solid state drive, a microSD media card slot, 802.11a/b/g/n/ac Wi-Fi, Bluetooth 4.0, a 5MP front-facing camera, an 8MP rear-facing camera with 1080p HD video recording, and dual integrated microphones. There are also built-in stereo speakers with Dolby audio. Windows 10 Pro is the installed operating system.

name: Moto G XT1039 8GB 4G LTE
description:
Motorola Moto G is a 2014 released LTE compatible smartphone from Motorola Mobility, now owned by Google. It features a mid-sized one-hand manageable 4.5-inch HD 720p touchscreen (1280 x 720p, 329ppi pixel density) and comes with impressive specs on a budget. It models a slightly curved back panel and is available in 8GB internal storage variant. 

Motorola Moto G comes with a 1.2 GHz Quad-Core processor. The processor is housed on the Qualcomm Snapdragon 400 chipset which embeds 1GB RAM as well. Its ROM features Android OS v4.4 (KitKat) preinstalled. The smartphone also sports an Adreno 305 GPU for graphics acceleration and splendid color reproduction.

A 5MP rear camera is part of the phone's design and works with HDR mode, panorama, burst shoot and slow-motion recording capabilities. Other specs of the Moto G include - Wi-Fi connectivity, 4G/LTE network support, Bluetooth 4.0, GPS/GLONASS, 50GB free Google Drive, integrated voice commands/control, HTML5 browser, 1.3MP HD 720p front cam, integration for social networks, Google integration, LED flash and a 2070mAh Li-Ion battery designed to last long entire day.

name: Motorola Moto G 3rd Gen Turbo XT1557 4G Dual sim - Black
description:
Meet the Moto G Turbo. Besides a powerful performance, it boasts a long-lasting battery, a lag-free user interface and IP67-certified durability.

The Moto G Turbo Edition is water and dust resistant (IP67 certified), so you don't have to worry about it whether you're chilling at the poolside or relaxing on the beach.

The Moto G Turbo Edition packs a 1.5 GHz Octa Core Snapdragon processor and 2 GB of RAM that boost its performance. The device is fast and lag-free, whether you're playing 3D games or multitasking between apps. This phone runs on the Android Lollipop v5.1.1 operating system.

This smartphone is powered by a 2470 mAh battery that packs enough juice to last through the day. However, if you still run out of battery, TurboCharge gives you up to 6 hours of usage from just 15 minutes of charging.

Capture the world around you with the 13 MP Quick Capture rear camera and save your precious moments for a lifetime. This camera includes enhanced software for fast image capture and video stabilisation. The 5 MP front camera is perfect for video calling and taking selfies.

Whether you're browsing through your gallery or playing 3D games, the 294 ppi, 12.7 cm (5) HD display of the Moto G Turbo Edition is a treat for your eyes. The tough Corning Gorilla Glass 3 keeps scratches and scuffs at bay.

name: OnePlus 3 A3000 Dual Sim 4G 64GB - Soft Gold (Flashed OS)
description:
It’s about time for a smartphone without compromises. A smartphone conceived and built by tech enthusiasts, hand-in-hand with users. A smartphone born from amazing technology, design, and innovation. 

It’s about time for the OnePlus 3. 

But, you shouldn’t take our word for it. You be the judge

Not all fast charging technologies are created equal. Dash Charge for the OnePlus 3 is faster, safer, cooler - and simply better - than any other charging technology available today. Providing over 60% charge in just 30 short minutes, Dash Charge changes the way we think about convenience.

16MP camera boasts lightning-fast shutter speed, snappy autofocus, and intelligent software to deliver an unmatched user experience. Cutting-edge noise reduction technology ensures that every shot is sharp and crisp, while two advanced stabilization methods prevent unwanted shakes and movements. Capture that stunning photo or video, every time.

6GB of LPDDR4 RAM into the OnePlus 3. Overkill? Maybe. Awesome? Yes. The top-of-the-line Qualcomm® Snapdragon™ 820 processor and Adreno™ 530 GPU make apps, games, and other intensive applications a breeze. Dual nano SIM support means you’ll always be connected, and with our vivid 5.5” Optic AMOLED display, all of that power under the hood is just as nice to look at as it is to use.

Feature

- Dash Charge

- Qualcomm® Snapdragon™ 820 Quad Core Processor

- 64GB ROM, 6GB RAM

- 5.5" Optic AMOLED Screen, 1920x1080, 401ppi

- 16MP Main Camera, f/2.0, phase detection autofocus, OIS, LED flash

- 8 MP Secondary Camera, f/2.0, 1/3.2" sensor size, 1.4 µm pixel size, 1080p

- USB 2.0, Type-C

- Dual nano-SIM slot

- Dirac HD Sound®

description:
It’s about time for a smartphone without compromises. A smartphone conceived and built by tech enthusiasts, hand-in-hand with users. A smartphone born from amazing technology, design, and innovation. 

It’s about time for the OnePlus 3. 

But, you shouldn’t take our word for it. You be the judge

Not all fast charging technologies are created equal. Dash Charge for the OnePlus 3 is faster, safer, cooler - and simply better - than any other charging technology available today. Providing over 60% charge in just 30 short minutes, Dash Charge changes the way we think about convenience.

16MP camera boasts lightning-fast shutter speed, snappy autofocus, and intelligent software to deliver an unmatched user experience. Cutting-edge noise reduction technology ensures that every shot is sharp and crisp, while two advanced stabilization methods prevent unwanted shakes and movements. Capture that stunning photo or video, every time.

6GB of LPDDR4 RAM into the OnePlus 3. Overkill? Maybe. Awesome? Yes. The top-of-the-line Qualcomm® Snapdragon™ 820 processor and Adreno™ 530 GPU make apps, games, and other intensive applications a breeze. Dual nano SIM support means you’ll always be connected, and with our vivid 5.5” Optic AMOLED display, all of that power under the hood is just as nice to look at as it is to use.

- 64GB, 6GB RAM

- 5.5" Optic AMOLED LCD Screen, 1920x1080, 401ppi

- 16 MP Rear Camera, f/2.0, phase detection autofocus, OIS, LED flash

- 8 MP Front Camera, f/2.0, 1/3.2" sensor size, 1.4 µm pixel size, 1080p

- Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, Wi-Fi Direct, DLNA, hotspot

- 3,000 mAh (non-removable)

- Dash Charge (5V 4A)

- OxygenOS based on Android™ Marshmallow

name: Samsung Galaxy A3 A310F 4G 16gb (2016) - Black
description:
High quality design - Combining metal and glass in a premium design usually found in flagship devices, the Galaxy A3 delivers a high quality finish that mixes strength and sophistication. The strong design brings convenience too, thanks to the Galaxy A3's slim body, while the vivid 4.7-inch display fills makes your pictures and videos even more eye-catching.

Fast and powerful - The Galaxy A3 has been designed to keep up with your busy schedule, using a high capacity battery to keep you going for longer. The Galaxy A3 won't let you down, and neither will our superfast network. Covering more than 95% of the UK population, our 4G network will let you stream, download an browse wherever you are.

Capture every moment - Capturing those special moments has never been so easy, with the Galaxy A3's quick launch feature giving you access to the 13MP camera in no time. The improved lens means that clear, bright photos are possible even in dark conditions. And on the 4G network that's 50% faster than any other, you'll be able to share your fantastic snaps in an instant.

Power when you need it - We use our smartphones for work, play and everything in between, so you need a device that performs no matter what you throw at it. That's where the Galaxy A3's powerful Quad Core processor comes in, giving you smooth multitasking abilities on the go. So whether you're downloading work documents on our superfast network, or streaming your favourite TV show, the Galaxy A3 won't let you down.

Feature

- Quad-core 1.5GHz Processor

- 16 GB, 1.5 GB RAM, microSD

- 4.7" Super AMOLED Screen 720 x 1280, 312ppi

- 13 MP Rear Camera, f/1.9, autofocus, LED flash

- 5 MP Front Camera, f/1.9

- Wi-Fi 802.11 b/g/n, Wi-Fi Direct, hotspot

- Bluetooth v4.1

- 2300 mAh

- Android OS, v5.1.1 (Lollipop)

name: Samsung Galaxy A5 A510FD Dual Sim 4G (2016 version)- Black
description:
The Galaxy A5 16GB Smartphone from Samsung delivers powerful performance and dual-SIM capability in a sleek aluminum uni-body design. The A5 Duos is powered by an octa-core 1.6 GHz ARM Cortex A53 processor and has 2GB of RAM in support. It also comes equipped with 16GB of storage and supports microSDXC cards up to 128GB. The A5 features built-in dual SIM card slots, which give you the ability to have two separate phone numbers on the same device. One of the SIM card slots functions as a hybrid slot that accepts microSDXC cards--however, because it's a hybrid slot, you won't be able to have a microSD card installed if you're using the A5 as a dual-SIM device.

Feature

- 5MP Front + 13MP Rear Cameras

- 2nd Generation 2016 Model

- 1.6 GHz Octa-Core CPU

- Hybrid Dual SIM Connectivity

- Android

name: Samsung Galaxy A7 A710FD Dual Sim 4G 16GB - Black
description:
The Samsung GALAXY A7 boasts an innovative, luxurious design and a stunning 5.5inch FHD sAMOLED display. You can feel the premium quality of the sleek full metal body in your hand.

The Alive Super Amoled Display and the Adapt Display deliver true-to-life colours on your Samsung GALAXY A7 which intelligently adapt to your surroundings. With its automatic Adjustable Audio, your Samsung GALAXY A7 will automatically increase or decrease the volume in response to the background noise around you.

With the Samsung GALAXY A7 you don't need to touch the button when taking selfies. Snap a selfie with your voice or palm. With the latest image detection and voice recognition software, the Samsung GALAXY A7 is taking the selfie to the next level. The new Wide Selfie function allows you to create a panorama-like selfie by merging three photos taken from the left/middle/right into one perfect group selfie. Now you can capture all your friends in one photo with up to 110° of range in portrait mode and 120° of range in landscape mode. 

The Samsung Galaxy A7 also offers Ultra Power Saving mode dramatically reduces battery consumption by shutting down unnecessary functions, ensuring your phone is available when you really need it.

Feature

- Octa-core 1.6 GHz Processor

- 16 GB, 3 GB RAM

- microSD, up to 128 GB

- 5.5 inches 1920 x 1080 (FHD) Super AMOLED 16M colors Screen, 401 ppi 

- 13 MP, f/1.9, OIS, autofocus, LED flash main camera, Full HD (1920 x 1080) @30fps

- 5 MP, f/1.9, 1080p secondary camera

- 4G, Dual Sim

- Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n, dual-band, WiFi Direct, hotspot

- Bluetooth v4.1, A2DP, EDR, LE

- Android OS, v5.1.1 (Lollipop)

name: Samsung Galaxy S7 G9300 32GB Dual SIM 4G LTE - White
description:
The Samsung Galaxy S7 32GB Smartphone offers a vibrant display, powerful performance, and high-quality optics in a sleek, water-resistant design. This smartphone incorporates 32GB of storage and is powered by an advanced multi-core chipset. Thanks to its integrated microSD expansion slot, users have the option of inserting microSDXC cards up to 200GB. For robust multi-tasking performance, this device also features 4GB of RAM, which allows it to efficiently run multiple apps simultaneously. 

The Samsung Galaxy S7 features an impressive 5.1" Super AMOLED screen, which is designed to produce bright images with robust color reproduction. The screen's detailed QHD 2560 x 1440 resolution enables vivid and detailed high-definition content. For photo capturing and video chatting, this smartphone features an f/1.7 5-megapixel front camera and an f/1.7 12-megapixel rear camera with dual-pixel technology. Dual-pixel technology is engineered to offer faster focusing times with reduced blur than previous generations. Optical image stabilization is onboard for shooting stability, and there's even an LED flash for taking pictures in low-light situations. Auto HDR allows you to enjoy photos with optimized exposure. On the video side, the rear camera allows you to capture detailed video at 4K resolution. 

The Samsung Galaxy S7 has Bluetooth 4.2 built-in for pairing with other Bluetooth-enabled devices, and dual-band 802.11ac Wi-Fi for high-speed Internet connectivity. Integrated Wi-Fi Direct and NFC give you the ability to connect to compatible devices for wirelessly sharing content like photos and music. The Samsung Galaxy 7 is also equipped with a large, non-removable 3000mAh battery that can be quickly recharged thanks to on-board fast charging technology.

- Android Marshmallow 6.0

name: Samsung Galaxy J5 J5007 4G Dual SIM 8GB - Gold - English Only
description:
Samsung has optimised the Galaxy J5 for a superior 4G experience with speeds up to 150 Mbps.

The Galaxy J5 features 5" HD Super AMOLED display and the proprietary Sound Alive technology that provide a holistic and immersive entertainment experience.

Samsung has ensured that the Galaxy J5 delivers superior multi-player gaming performance by powering it with 64-bit Quad-Core processor along with 1.5 GB of RAM.

With the launch of Galaxy J5, Samsung has also redefined the selfie experience for consumers with a powerful 5 MP front camera coupled with a front facing flash for great selfies in any lighting condition. The smartphone is equipped with a 13 MP AF primary camera to provide imaging capabilities that are powerful enough to fulfil every shutterbugs needs.

The slim and light Galaxy J5 comes with a user-friendly design philosophy to enable users with a comfortable grip while operating or playing a game on the phone. With a slim design, the Galaxy J5 measures up to 7.9 mm and comes with anti-smudge anodised CMF coating, which gives the devices a premium and stylish feel.

name: Samsung Galaxy J5 J500HD 3G Dual SIM 8GB - Gold - English Only
description:
The Samsung Galaxy J5 8GB Smartphone offers powerful performance and high-definition image quality. Designed for used in North and South America, this smartphone is powered by the Snapdragon 410 chipset with consists of a 1.2 GHz quad-core processor. The Galaxy J5 also has 1.5GB of RAM for multi-tasking. This model stores up to 8GB of data and features a microSDXC slot, which supports memory cards up to 128GB for added storage capacity. The smartphone's micro-USB 2.0 interface allows you to connect the device for mass-storage purposes and also serves as a charging port. 

The Samsung Galaxy J5 has a 5.0" Super AMOLED screen and an HD 1280 x 720 native resolution for viewing detailed content. For photo capturing and video chatting, this smartphone features a 5-megapixel front camera and an f/1.9 13-megapixel rear camera. The front and rear cameras are also accompanied by an LED flash for capturing images in low-light situations. 

High-speed Internet access is enabled by the smartphone's integrated 802.11b/g/n Wi-Fi connectivity. Bluetooth 4.1 is also built-in for pairing with other Bluetooth-enabled devices. Built-in GPS allows you to utilize Google location and maps services, as well as receive turn-by-turn directions. The Samsung Galaxy J5 has a large, removable 2600mAh battery that can deliver up to 18 hours of 3G talk time.

- 8GB Storage Capacity & 1.5GB of RAM

- 5.0" Super AMOLED Display

- microSDXC Expansion up to 128GB

description:
The Sony Xperia Z3+ 4G E6533 is slimmer than ever at just 6.9 mm, and incredibly light in your hand. In fact, if it wasn’t so nice to look at, you could almost forget you were holding it. The Sony Xperia Z3+ 4G E6533 carries our renowned waterproof* design, so you can meet the day head-on – no matter what kind of day it is. The IP65/IP68 rating means downpours aren’t a problem. Nor is sand, spills or an accidental dip in the sink.

 

The Sony Xperia Z3+ 4G E6533’s camera excels where other smartphone cameras disappoint. Indoors, at night, or when the sun’s behind your subject. With the best Sony camera technologies, your shots end up clear and sharp no matter where you are.

 

We’ve added some of our most innovative camera technologies to the Sony Xperia Z3+ 4G E6533’s wide-angle front camera, like Superior Auto and SteadyShot with Intelligent Active Mode. The result is sharper-than-ever selfies, steady front-camera videos and ‘groupies’ that fit everyone in the frame.

 

Get directions at midnight, marathon-watch your favourite show, or skip the charger in your overnight bag. The Sony Xperia Z3+ 4G E6533’s incredible battery life brings you up to two days of power, so you can do more with every charge. This Android™ mobile boasts the industry’s most powerful processor for top speeds and lag-free performance. Using the very latest smart connectivity technologies your Sony Xperia Z3+ 4G E6533 will reach up to 50% faster Wi-Fi speeds than previous products. So file transfers and media streaming is faster and smoother than ever.

- Stunning landscapes to stunner selfies – now twice the camera excellence

name: Samsung Galaxy Note 5 N920C 32GB 4G - Gold
description:
Samsung introduces its new flagship phablet with this impressive Samsung Note 5 32GB. Boasting a full metal-and-glass construction, the rounded slender device settles perfectly and can be held comfortably in one hand. The phablet models a 5.7 inches Super AMOLED capacitive touchscreen with a QHD (2560 x 1440p) screen resolution. Supporting multitouch functionality, the screen packs a massive 518 pixels per inch of the screen allowing for stunningly clear visuals. Also, it features Corning Gorilla Glass 4 protection that is capable of deterring bumps and scratches.

The device’s internal hardware comprises of a powerful Exynos 7420 Octa-core CPU featuring four 2.1GHz core and four 1.5GHz core processors. It is more energy-efficient than its predecessor reducing heat and power consumption. For storage, the phablet has a 4 GB RAM that enables extraordinarily fast multitasking and app processing while the present 32 GB of ROM has Android OS, v5.1.1 (Lollipop) pre-installed. In terms of camera optics, it has a f/1.9 16-megapixel rear camera with OIS, face Detection, AutoHDR, and a 5-megapixel front snapper. Capturing images can be taken to the next level with the ability to shoot in RAW in Pro Mode. With this device, using the S Pen has also been simplified; simply pressing the device brings the pen out.

Other prominent features include- UHD 4K video recording, Image stabilization (Rear); Recording Mode(Rear): Fast Motion, Slow Motion, Video Collage; Recording Mode(Front): Video Collage; Live Broadcast, Wi-Fi, USB 2.0, Bluetooth v4.2, ANT+, GLONASS, GPS, NFC, 4G LTE, Noise Cancellation, Accelerometer, Barometer, Fingerprint Sensor, Gyro Sensor, Geomagnetic Sensor, Hall Sensor, HR Sensor, Light Sensor, Proximity Sensor, and 3000 mAh Li-ion battery.

Feature

- 5.7" QHD (2560 x 1440 pixels) Super AMOLED display with 518ppi

- 64-bit Exynos 7420 chipset with 14nm architecture; octa-core CPU (quad 2.1GHz & quad 1.5GHz), Mali-T760MP8 GPU

- 4GB of LPDDR4 RAM; 32GB of UFS 2.0 flash memory

- 16MP f/1.9 camera with OIS; Auto HDR; 4K video capture; IR white balance detection sensor, Pro mode and RAW shooting

- 5MP f/1.9 front-facing camera

- Fingerprint scanner

- Redesigned clickable S-Pen

- Wired and wireless Quick Charging

- 3,000mAh non-removable battery; Qi (WPC) and PMA wireless charging support

- Android 5.1.1 Lollipop with TouchWiz UX

Samsung Galaxy Note 5 N920C 32GB 4G - Gold

name: Samsung Galaxy S6 edge G925F 32GB SIM FREE / UNLOCKED - Black
description:
Inspired by the works of glassblowers and artisan metalsmiths, the Samsung Galaxy S6 edge represents a seamless fusion of glass and metal. Make a breathtaking design statement with the world’s first dual-edge display, beautiful curves and radiant glass surfaces that reflect a wide spectrum of dazzling colours.

 

Add some colour to your interactions with the Samsung Galaxy S6 edge. Colour-code the five people you care most about and simply tab a contact’s colour on the edge display to call, text or email them. Thanks to innovative colour-coded notifications, you can easily see who is trying to get in touch, even when your device is upside down.

 

Both the Samsung Galaxy S6 edge’s front and rear cameras feature higher resolution and F1.9 aperture, allowing you to take clearer images wherever you are. Press the home button twice to go straight into camera mode ? and never miss an important moment again.

 

With super-fast boot up and app launching, the Samsung Galaxy S6 edge gives you unbeatable results and improved energy efficiency. Its 64-bit architecture, LPDDR4 and advanced GPU delivers truly powerful performance, letting you take multitasking and multimedia functions to the next level.

 

Equipped with a 5.1” Quad HD (2560X1440) Super AMOLED display, the Samsung Galaxy S6 edge provides an impeccably sharp viewing experience, and its adaptive display provides unbeatable clarity both indoors and outside. Improved brightness levels and pixel density let you take superb images wherever you are.

 

Enjoy unprecedented peace of mind with the Samsung Galaxy S6 edge’s powerful security solutions: KNOX, a fingerprint scanner. The new Smart Manager application lets you check an array of useful information on battery status, storage, RAM, security and more at a glance.

Feature

- World’s first dual-edge display

- 5.1-inch Quad HD Super AMOLED Display 2560 x 1440, 577 PPI

- The F1.9 lenses and high resolution sensors on both front (5MP) and rear (16MP) cameras

- With Auto Real-time High Dynamic Range (HDR), Smart Optical Image Stabilization (OIS) and IR Detect White Balance

- Quick Launch” feature give users fast, direct access to the camera from any screen in just 0.7 seconds

- Thin (7 mm) and lightweight (132 g)

- Octacore processor, 3GB Ram

- With Samsung security solutions: KNOX, a fingerprint scanner.

name: Samsung Galaxy S6 G920F 4G LTE 32GB SIM FREE / UNLOCKED - Black
description:
Samsung Galaxy S6 G920F 4G LTE 32GB (Unlocked) Mobile Phones

- f/1.9 16 MP Rear + 5 MP Front Cameras

- Optical Image Stabilization

- 4K UHD Video Recording

- Samsung Exynos 7420 Octa-Core Chipset

- 5.1" Super AMOLED Display

- Unibody Metal Design


The Samsung Galaxy S6 SM-G920F Smartphone offers powerful performance and high-quality optics in a sleek, sealed design. This smartphone incorporates 3GB of RAM, and is powered by the Samsung Exynos 7420 chipset. This high-performance, 64-bit chipset consists of 1.5 GHz and 2.1 GHz ARM quad-core CPUs for robust processing and multi-tasking. This architecture allows you to fluidly navigate the Android Lollipop operating system. 

 

The Samsung Galaxy S6 features a notable 5.1" Super AMOLED screen, which is designed to produce bright images with robust color reproduction. The screen's detailed QHD 2560 x 1440 resolution enables vivid and detailed high-definition content. For photo capturing and video chatting, this smartphone features an f/1.9 5-megapixel front camera and an f/1.9 16-megapixel rear camera. Optical image stabilization is onboard for shooting stability, and there's even an LED flash for taking pictures in low-light situations. On the video side, the rear camera allows you to capture detailed video at 4K resolution. 

 

The Samsung Galaxy S6 has Bluetooth 4.1 built-in for pairing with other Bluetooth-enabled devices, and dual-band 802.11ac Wi-Fi for high-speed Internet connectivity. Integrated Wi-Fi Direct and NFC give you the ability to connect-to compatible devices for wirelessly sharing content like photos and music. The Samsung Galaxy 6 is equipped with a non-removable 2550mAh battery that's designed to delivers hours of enjoyment before charging is needed.

description:
The Samsung Galaxy S7 edge 32GB Smartphone offers a vibrant display with a dual curve edged screen, powerful performance, and high-quality optics in a sleek, water-resistant design. This smartphone incorporates 32GB of storage and is powered by an advanced multi-core chipset. name: Sony Xperia Z5 Dual 4G E6683 - Gold
description:
Xperia Z5 brings the best camera in a leading smartphone, with an elegant waterproof design.

Xperia Z5 features Sony's brand new large 1/2.3 Exmor RS™ for mobile 23MP sensor and F2.0 G Lens – it's Sony's first completely re-imagined smartphone camera module since Xperia Z1, designed with Sony's interchangeable lens camera a™ technology for clear, vivid imagery every time.

Designed by leading creatives at Sony's Creative Center studios in Sweden and Japan, Xperia Z5 presents a svelte continuous plate form, with a metal frame and frosted glass back. It's striking, comfortable to hold and waterproof for everyday convenience.

Xperia Z5 is powered by the Qualcomm Snapdragon 810 processor, featuring octa-core CPUs, 64 bit capabilities and ultra-fast 4G LTE speeds, letting you reach new levels of performance for video, photography and gaming. Whether you're multi-tasking over Wi-Fi or the latest 4G network, the Xperia Z5 delivers the speed you need. Download email with attachments in seconds and enjoy video streaming with no delays or unwanted buffering.

Powerful smartphone features demand smart power management, Xperia Z5 is equipped with Sony's incredible battery stamina and innovative power-saving technology, which gives you superior long-lasting battery performance. With Qualcomm® Quick Charge™ 2.0 enabled on this device, you can get 5.5 hours usage with just 10 minutes of charging with a certified Quick Charge™ 2.0 charger.

name: Samsung Galaxy S7 edge G9350 4G Dual sim 32GB - Olympic Edition
description:
Stay focused with this unlocked Samsung Galaxy S7 Olympic Games Limited Edition smartphone. A slim profile and IP68 rating keep it safe in your pocket, even when it's raining, and a powerful dual-pixel camera delivers outstanding low-light images. Keep on going with the massive battery, expandable memory and total network freedom of this unlocked Samsung Galaxy S7 Olympic Games Limited Edition smartphone. 

Olympic design Limited Edition

Custom design and UI inspired by the Olympic colors with unique messaging application and premium travel case.

Qualcomm Snapdragon 820 processor

Quad-core 2.2GHz processor and 4GB of RAM deliver outstanding overall performance for opening and running applications, flipping through menus, running home screens and more.

Android 6.0 Marshmallow OS

Offers a fresh, fast platform to help you stay connected and productive while you're on the go.

4G LTE speed

Provides fast Web connection for downloading apps, streaming content and staying connected with social media.

5.5" Quad HD Super AMOLED touch screen

Extra-large screen is matched with a slim body to comfortably fit in your hand. Offers 16:9 cinema-like screen ratio that's perfect for viewing of videos, photos and games.

12MP rear-facing camera for 2160p 4K UHD video recording

Dedicated light sensor enables the camera to capture more light in dark environments for better pictures. Also includes a front-facing 5MP camera for self-portraits and video.

32GB internal memory plus microSD slot

Provides plenty of storage space for your contacts, music, photos, apps and more. Expand storage up to 200GB by adding a microSD card (sold separately).

Use your smartphone as a mobile hotspot

Share your 4G data connection with other compatible wireless devices.*

Take things at your own pace with the Easy Mode setting

Simplify your home screen with bigger icons and your favorite apps.

Ultra Power Saving mode lets you keep your phone powered on for longer in between charges

This mode changes your screen to black and white and shuts down all unnecessary features to dramatically minimize battery consumption.

Heart rate sensor lets you measure your heart rate through your fingertip

Plus, monitor your health consistently with the custom services offered by S Health. Log and check your exercise, food intake and heart rate in real time.

Your fingerprint keeps your phone secure

Swipe your finger on the backside sensor panel to unlock your phone.

Access to Google Play

Browse and download apps, magazines, books, movies, and television programs directly to your phone.

Listen to your favorite tunes

Store and play your MP3 files on your phone.

The Samsung Galaxy S7 edge has Bluetooth 4.2 built-in for pairing with other Bluetooth-enabled devices, and dual-band 802.11ac Wi-Fi for high-speed Internet connectivity. The Samsung Galaxy 7 edge is equipped with a large, non-removable 3600mAh battery that can be quickly recharged thanks to on-board fast charging technology.

name: Sony Xperia Z5 Dual 4G E6683 - White
description:
Xperia Z5 brings the best camera in a leading smartphone, with an elegant waterproof design.

Xperia Z5 features Sony's brand new large 1/2.3 Exmor RS™ for mobile 23MP sensor and F2.0 G Lens – it's Sony's first completely re-imagined smartphone camera module since Xperia Z1, designed with Sony's interchangeable lens camera a™ technology for clear, vivid imagery every time.

Designed by leading creatives at Sony's Creative Center studios in Sweden and Japan, Xperia Z5 presents a svelte continuous plate form, with a metal frame and frosted glass back. It's striking, comfortable to hold and waterproof for everyday convenience.

Xperia Z5 is powered by the Qualcomm Snapdragon 810 processor, featuring octa-core CPUs, 64 bit capabilities and ultra-fast 4G LTE speeds, letting you reach new levels of performance for video, photography and gaming. Whether you're multi-tasking over Wi-Fi or the latest 4G network, the Xperia Z5 delivers the speed you need. Download email with attachments in seconds and enjoy video streaming with no delays or unwanted buffering.

Powerful smartphone features demand smart power management, Xperia Z5 is equipped with Sony's incredible battery stamina and innovative power-saving technology, which gives you superior long-lasting battery performance. With Qualcomm® Quick Charge™ 2.0 enabled on this device, you can get 5.5 hours usage with just 10 minutes of charging with a certified Quick Charge™ 2.0 charger.

The 7.0" Tab A 8GB Tablet from Samsung delivers powerful performance and wireless content sharing in a sleek, modern design. This tablet is powered by a quad-core 1.3 GHz Snapdragon 410 processor and has 1.5GB of RAM. It comes equipped with 8GB of built-in storage, a micro-USB port for data sharing, and a microSDXC card slot that supports up to 200GB of additional storage capacity. For high-speed Internet connectivity, Wi-Fi is built-in. Bluetooth 4.0 connectivity is also integrated for wireless pairing with compatible devices, such as headphones and other Bluetooth-enabled accessories.

This Galaxy Tab A houses a 7.0" IPS capacitive touchscreen display with a 1280 x 800 resolution for viewing all your favorite content. Additionally, the Tab A is equipped with a dual camera array: a front facing 2-megapixel camera and a rear-facing 5-megapixel camera. Photog-friendly features, such panoramic shots and the ability to create animated GIFs from a picture series, are also included. 

A micro-USB interface is built-in for mass storage connections and charging the device. The embedded 4000mAh battery is designed to offer hours of enjoyment before recharging is needed. The Galaxy Tab A comes with the Android 5.1.1 Lollipop operating system, which is designed for fluid and intuitive multi-touch navigation.

description:

With the Super AMOLED and high resolution display, content looks better. Whether you're watching your favourite shows, organising your photos, or crafting a presentation, the Tab Pro S is designed to deliver the best viewing experience available.

With LTE compatibility and Xbox One streaming, your gaming can go anywhere you go. The Samsung Galaxy TabPro S allows you to stay connected to both work and play.

The TabPro S is designed to provide full desktop replacement. With Windows 10 and 4G/LTE connectivity, computing power can be provided on the move. Additionally the Tab Pro S can be adapted to work with most desktop monitors - creating a full desktop environment.

Unlike many 2-in-1 devices, the Tab Pro S comes with keyboard and track pad included. The keyboard is a fuller size creating a more familiar computing experience.

Pairing your Samsung Galaxy Smartphone to your Galaxy TabPro S creates an integrated device environment. Use your Smartphone as an authentication tool - unlocking your screen when the two devices are in close proximity, and share files between each device with SideSync.

Designed to deliver business continuity, the TabPro S delivers up to 10.5 hours of battery life and can charge from zero to full in just two and a half hours.

 

Feature

- 2.2 GHz Dual Core Processor

- 4GB of RAM

- 12" FHD+ Super AMOLED Display

- 2160 x 1440 Screen Resolution

- 128GB SSD

- 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac Wi-Fi, Bluetooth 4.1

- USB Type-C 3.1

- 5MP Rear Camera + 5MP Front Camera

- Windows 10

name: Samsung Gear 360 SM-C200 Cam VR Camera Dual Lens
description:
Record and capture 360-degree videos and images with the Gear 360 Spherical VR Camera from Samsung. This travel-friendly device is equipped with dual 15MP fisheye lenses that enable users to capture hi-res (3840 x 1920) 360-degree videos and 30MP still images. Each of the Gear's lenses capture 180-degrees horizontally and vertically, allowing you stitch together a seamless 360-degree view of the world around you. You can also use just one of the Gear's lenses to capture a wide-angle video at 2560 x 1440 resolution or a 5MP still image. In addition to shooting vivid day images, the Gear 360's bright, f/2.0 lenses enable the camera to work in low-light environments.

 

CompatibilityGalaxy S6, S6 edge, S6 edge+, Note 5, S7, S7 edge with the Samsung Gear 360 app
PCs with the Gear 360 ActionDirector software
Sensor2 x 15 MP CMOS
Lens Aperturef/2.0
Field of View180° per lens
ChipsetDRIMe5s
Video FormatMP4 (H.265)
Video ResolutionDual Cam: 3840 x 1920 at 30 fps
Single Cam: 2560 x 1440 at 30 fps
Image FormatJPEG
Image ResolutionDual Cam: 7776 x 3888 (30 MP)
Single Cam: 3072 x 1728 (5 MP)
AudioCodec: MP3/AAC/AAC+/eAAC+ 
Format: MP3, M4A, AAC, OGG
Memory1 GB built-in RAM 
microSD card up to 128 GB

WiFi Direct

NFC

name: SONY Xperia C4 Dual E5333 - Black
description:
The Sony Xperia C4 is equipped with a front cam that's based around a 5MP sensor, a wide-angle (25mm wide) front camera lens, and a "soft" LED flash. Of course, this is a Sony phone, so not all the action is up front. The rear camera is a 13MP unit driven by Sony's own Exmor sensor. One-upping the newly announced Xperia Z4 by 0.3 inches, the Xperia C4 has a 5.5-inch 1080p IPS LCD display, complete with Sony's TV imaging technologies - Bravia engine and super vivid mode. The selfie phone doesn't compromise on design either, employing that beautiful glass and aluminum build. Sony didn't make this one water and dust-proof, but hey, at least the screen is scratch-resistant! On the hardware side, an octa-core 1.7GHz CPU (probably the MediaTek MT6752) runs the show, aided by an ARM Mali-T760 GPU and 2GB of RAM. A 2600mAh battery is crammed in, providing at least eight hours of video playback according to Sony.

- 16 GB, 2 GB RAM, MicroSD

- 5.5" IPS LCD, 1920x1080, 401ppi, Scratch-resistant

- 5 MP Front Camera, f/2.2, 720p, LED flash

- Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n, Wi-Fi Direct, DLNA, hotspot

- Bluetooth v4.1, A2DP, aptX

- Dual SIM (Nano-SIM, dual stand-by)

As the name implies, the Sony Xperia X Compact is for those who seek a light, reasonably small, pocket-friendly Android handset. It is also a phone not to be underestimated, as it combines a respectable amount of processing power with Sony's latest camera technologies. The 23MP shooter at the back is backed by an array of sensors aiding it in nailing the perfect focus and color balance. At the same time, the large image sensor and Sony's newest algorithms deliver superior detail. And with a fast-charging 2700mAh battery, the Xperia X Compact has enough power to last you through the day.

- 32Gb, 3GB RAM, microSD

name: Sony Xperia XA Ultra F3216 16GB Dual sim Mobile Phone - Graphite Black
description:
The Sony Xperia XA Ultra is powered by octa-core MediaTek MT6755 processor and it comes with 3GB of RAM. The phone packs 16GB of internal storage that can be expanded up to 200GB via a microSD card. As far as the cameras are concerned, the Sony Xperia XA Ultra packs a 21.5-megapixel primary camera on the rear and a 16-megapixel front shooter for selfies. 

The Sony Xperia XA Ultra runs Android 6.0 and is powered by a 2700mAh removable battery. It measures 164 x 79 x 8.40 (height x width x thickness) and weighs 202.00 grams. 

The Sony Xperia XA Ultra is a single SIM (GSM) smartphone that accepts a Nano-SIM. Connectivity options include Wi-Fi, GPS, Bluetooth, NFC, FM, 4G. Sensors on the phone include Proximity sensor, Ambient light sensor, Accelerometer, and Gyroscope. 

Feature

- 64-bit MediaTek MT6755 Octa Core Processor

- 16GB, 3GB RAM, mocroSD

- 6" IPS LCD Screen, Mobile BRAVIA engine 2, 1920x1080, 367ppi

- 21.5 MP Rear Camera, Exmor RS, Flash: LED

- 16 MP Front Camera, Video: HD 1080p

- Bluetooth: 4.1

- Wi-Fi: 802.11 a/b/g/n

- nano-SIM, Dual Sim

- 2700 mAh

- Google Android 6.0 (Marshmallow)

description:
Xperia XZ has been tested under Ingress Protection rating IP65/68, so don’t worry if you get caught in the rain or want to wash off dirt under a tap water, but remember all ports and attached covers should be firmly closed. You should not put the device completely underwater; or expose it to seawater, salt water, chlorinated water or liquids such as drinks. Abuse and improper use of device will invalidate warranty. Note the Xperia XZ has a capless USB port to connect and charge. The USB port needs to be completely dry before charging.

Feature

- Qualcomm Snapdragon 820 MSM8996 Quad Core Processor

- 64 GB, 3GB Ram, microSD

- 5.2", TRILUMINOS Display with X-Reality, 1080 x 1920 pixels

- Wi-Fi: 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, 2.4 GHz/5 GHz, Bluetooth v4.2,

- USB Type-C

- IP65/68

- 2900 mAh

- Google Android 6.0 (Marshmallow)

name: Sony Xperia Z3 Tablet Compact 16GB 4G SGP621 White
description:
The Sony Xperia Z3 Tablet Compact 16GB 4G - SGP621 is a mid-sized Android device that serves as your portable work and entertainment companion. The 6.4mm thin sleek looking gadget takes the power of Xperia Z3 and turns it into a tablet without any compromise on hardware specs. It features an 8.0-inch Opti Contrast Full HD IPS touchscreen with a TRILUMINOUS LCD and Sony's spectacular X-Reality technology. This amalgam makes it a powerful unit for displaying top notch graphics whether you're watching a movie, playing games or browsing the internet. Living up to Xperia standards, the device comes with the highest rating for waterproofing (IP65/68). 

The Sony Xperia Z3 Tablet Compact 16GB 4G - SGP621 is designed for high quality Hi-res audio streaming. Perfect for music lovers, it features Sony's superior noise cancelling technology and provides stereo frontal speakers. As far as internal hardware specs go, Qualcomm's Snapdragon 801 processor is the heart of the Sony Xperia Z3 Tablet Compact 16GB 4G - SGP621. It boasts a clock rate of 2.5GHz and works in conjunction with 3GB built-in RAM for stunningly smooth app operation. Its 16GB internal ROM has Google's Android OS v4.4 (KitKat) preloaded with full access to Play Store. 

The Sony Xperia Z3 Tablet Compact 16GB 4G - SGP621 comprises of an 8.1MP Exmor RS primary camera at the back. It also sports a 2.2MP Exmor R front cam. Other notable specs of the tablet are - LTE network support, Wi-Fi connectivity, Miracast, Wi-Fi Direct, NFC, DLNA, Bluetooth 4.0, MHL 3.0, Adreno 330 GPU with 3D gaming support, microUSB interface, microSD card slot (up to 128GB supported), PS4 Remote Play support, Clear Audio+ sound, VPT Sony Surround Sound technology and a 4500mAh battery with STAMINA mode for power saving. 

Feature

- Quality craftsmanship in a slim aluminium frame

- Dive deeper with a tablet that's waterproof up to 1.5m

- Capture every moment with an 8MP camera

- TRILUMINOS™ Display for the widest spectrum of colours

- Always a great viewing angle with IPS technology

- Experience legendary sound with High-Res Audio

- Razor-sharp images with X-Reality for mobile

- Snapdragon™ 801 processor – incredible speed and power

- Ultra-fast downloads with 4G technology

- Activate Battery STAMINA Mode and keep your battery going longer – without major compromise

description:
The Sony Xperia Z3+ 4G E6533 is slimmer than ever at just 6.9 mm, and incredibly light in your hand. In fact, if it wasn’t so nice to look at, you could almost forget you were holding it. The Sony Xperia Z3+ 4G E6533 carries our renowned waterproof* design, so you can meet the day head-on – no matter what kind of day it is. The IP65/IP68 rating means downpours aren’t a problem. Nor is sand, spills or an accidental dip in the sink.

 

The Sony Xperia Z3+ 4G E6533’s camera excels where other smartphone cameras disappoint. Indoors, at night, or when the sun’s behind your subject. With the best Sony camera technologies, your shots end up clear and sharp no matter where you are.

 

We’ve added some of our most innovative camera technologies to the Sony Xperia Z3+ 4G E6533’s wide-angle front camera, like Superior Auto and SteadyShot with Intelligent Active Mode. The result is sharper-than-ever selfies, steady front-camera videos and ‘groupies’ that fit everyone in the frame.

 

Get directions at midnight, marathon-watch your favourite show, or skip the charger in your overnight bag. The Sony Xperia Z3+ 4G E6533’s incredible battery life brings you up to two days of power, so you can do more with every charge. This Android™ mobile boasts the industry’s most powerful processor for top speeds and lag-free performance. Using the very latest smart connectivity technologies your Sony Xperia Z3+ 4G E6533 will reach up to 50% faster Wi-Fi speeds than previous products. So file transfers and media streaming is faster and smoother than ever.

name: Apple iPad Pro 128GB Wifi -Space gray
description:
While the size of the Apple 128GB iPad Pro may be a bit daunting, its 12.9" Retina Display will quickly remove your doubts, thanks to its 2732 x 2048 screen resolution, 264 pixels per inch (ppi), and 5.6 million pixels. Supporting high resolution videos and photos, you'll be able to experience vivid colors and deep black levels. The Retina Display delivers greater contrast, more uniform brightness, and improved energy efficiency through photo alignment technology, oxide TFT, and variable refresh rate.

Powering the large Retina display is the Apple A9X chip with a M9 motion coprocessor. The 3rd generation 64-bit chip can pump out desktop-class CPU performance and console-class graphics. The faster performance allows you to multitask with ease, using iOS 9 features, such as Picture in Picture, Slide Over, and Split View. Also, the iPad Pro is capable of playing three simultaneous 4K video streams in iMovie.

The iPad Pro comes with iOS 9 installed, which features proactive assistance as well as powerful search and improved Siri features, all while protecting your privacy. There are multitasking features designed specifically for iPad which allow you to use multiple apps simultaneously, and built-in apps become more powerful with a redesigned Notes app, detailed transit information in Maps, and the added News app. The foundation of iOS is even stronger with software updates that require less space to install and advanced security features to further protect your device.

While the Retina Display of the iPad Pro features multi-touch capabilities, Apple does offer alternative ways of interacting with the iPad Pro. The Apple Pencil is an optional accessory that can capture twice as many data points as your finger for greater precision. Force and tilt sensors transmit precise information to the iPad Pro so you can intuitively lay down lines of varying thickness and opacity. The Smart Keyboard is another optional accessory that connects to the Smart Connector on the iPad Pro, which means you don't have to use Bluetooth. The Smart Keyboard has Apple's dome switches for precision typing.

Feature

- 12.9" Multi-Touch Retina Display

- 2732 x 2048 Screen Resolution (264 ppi)

- Apple A9X 64-bit SoC with M9 Coprocessor

- 802.11ac Wi-Fi, Bluetooth 4.2

- Front 1.2MP FaceTime HD Camera

- Rear 8MP iSight Camera

- Four-Speaker Audio Design

- Touch ID Fingerprint Sensor

- Lightning Connector, Smart Connector

- iOS 9

description:
Xperia Z5 brings the best camera in a leading smartphone, with an elegant waterproof design.

Xperia Z5 features Sony's brand new large 1/2.3 Exmor RS™ for mobile 23MP sensor and F2.0 G Lens – it's Sony's first completely re-imagined smartphone camera module since Xperia Z1, designed with Sony's interchangeable lens camera a™ technology for clear, vivid imagery every time.

Xperia Z5 is powered by the Qualcomm Snapdragon 810 processor, featuring octa-core CPUs, 64 bit capabilities and ultra-fast 4G LTE speeds, letting you reach new levels of performance for video, photography and gaming. name: Apple ipad Pro 9.7" 128GB Wifi -Rose Gold
description:
Apple returns to the classic iPad form factor with the 9.7" iPad Pro. The display features a 2048 x 1536 resolution at 264 pixels per inch (ppi). Using a DCI-P3 color space, the iPad Pro display provides a wider color gamut than standard sRGB displays. And with more available colors, the images will appear more vivid and reveal greater detail. The Retina Display delivers greater contrast, more uniform brightness, and improved energy efficiency through photo alignment technology, an oxide TFT panel, display lamination, an anti-reflective coating, and a variable refresh rate. The iPad Pro also features True Tone display, which uses advanced four-channel ambient light sensors to dynamically adjust white balance and brightness.

Powering the 9.7" Retina display is the Apple A9X chip with a M9 motion coprocessor. The 3rd generation 64-bit chip can pump out desktop-class CPU performance and console-class graphics. The faster performance allows you to multitask with ease, using iOS 9 features, such as Picture in Picture, Slide Over, and Split View. Also, the iPad Pro is capable of playing three simultaneous 4K video streams in iMovie. The iPad Pro also features 128GB of storage.

The rear 12MP iSight camera has an f/2.2 aperture and a True Tone flash. It can shoot Live Photos and 4K video as well as Full HD 1080p slow-motion video and panoramas up to 63MP in size. The 5MP front-facing camera allows you to FaceTime in HD with friends and family.

The iPad Pro comes with iOS 9 installed, which features proactive assistance as well as powerful search and improved Siri features, all while protecting your privacy. There are the aforementioned multitasking features for iPad, which allow you to use multiple apps simultaneously, as well as improvements to built-in apps. The Notes app has been redesigned, the Maps app gives detailed transit information, and the News app adds another way to keep up with the times. The foundation of iOS is even stronger, with software updates that require less space to install and advanced security features to further protect your device.

While the Retina Display of the iPad Pro features multi-touch capabilities, Apple does offer an alternative ways of interacting with the iPad Pro. The Apple Pencil is an optional accessory that can capture twice as many data points as your finger for greater precision. Force and tilt sensors transmit precise information to the iPad Pro, so you can intuitively lay down lines of varying thickness and opacity. The Smart Keyboard is another optional accessory that connects to the Smart Connector on the iPad Pro, which means you don't have to use Bluetooth. The Smart Keyboard has Apple's dome switches for precision typing.luded for streamlined installation.

Feature

- 9.7-inch Retina display with anti-reflective coating (diagonal)

- A9X third-generation chip with 64-bit desktopclass architecture

- Touch ID fingerprint sensor

- 12MP iSight camera with 4K video

- 5MP FaceTime HD camera

- 802.11ac Wi-Fi with MIMO

- Up to 10 hours of battery life

- Four speaker audio

name: Sony Xperia Z5 Premium 4G E6833 Dual sim - Chrome
description:
Sony Xperia Z5 premium is the brand’s claim for the first globally known 4K phablet / smartphone. It is also the next step up from the original Z5 model. Premium is the keyword here and may be used more than once, for emphasis. This phablet style phone is in its Dual SIM version here, and has a decidedly smart rectangular look, with premium metal side framing and a mirror shine-finish back piece. It is IP65 and IP68 waterproof up to 1.5m deep for 30 minutes, and dust-closed for superior protection.

The 5.5 inch, IPS LCD screen has a 3840 x 2160 Ultra HD resolution, and uses the exclusive Triluminos display, X-Reality, and a Dynamic Contrast Enhancer for utmost enhanced viewing. It is bound in scratch proof glass with an oleophobic coating for maximum clarity. A security activated, fingerprint sensor enhanced power button lays on the side for the owner only.

Matching inside and out, are premium internal electronics to handle all aspects of the phone. That is a combination of the 64 bit Qualcomm Snapdragon Octa core processor, comprised of a 1.5GHz quad core and 2GHz quad core processor, with an Adreno 430 GPU, 3GB of RAM, and 32GB of storage memory. It can expand its storage using its micro SD slot, with provision for up to 200GB of removable storage. Everything is managed and organized with the Google Android™ 5.1 Lollipop OS.

There are two cameras for action: a main rear 23 Megapixel camera with a 1/2.3 MP Sony Exmor RS sensor, with Hybrid Auto focusing, 5x Image zoom, 8x Digital zoom, 24mm Wide Angle G lens, ISO 12800 image / 3200 video setting, exclusive Steady Shot / Intelligent Active Mode video stabilization, 4K for video capture, and with a Pulse type LED flash unit; the selfie-optimized 5MP front camera with an Exmor R sensor, exclusive Steady Shot / Intelligent Active Mode video stabilization, and a 25mm wide angle lens.

Among the connectivity formats available for this phone are 4G LTE cat 6, 3G, 2G, GPRS, EDGE, Wi-Fi 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac, dual-band, Wi-Fi Direct, DLNA, hotspot, MIMO, ANT+, PS4 Remote Play / Play Memories, Bluetooth v4.1 / A2DP /apt-X, NFC, FM Radio with RDS, a micro USB v2.0 port (MHL3 TV output), USB host, and a 3.5mm audio jack. A fully charged unit can provide up to 48 hours of usage, with an improved Quick Charge capability for faster recharging periods.

Beyond these, this phone has enhanced audio for music and multimedia, using the following features and modes: compatibility for LPCM, FLAC, ALAC, DSD formats; DSEE HX, LDAC, Digital Noise Cancelling, Clear Audio +, S Force Front Surround Sound, Auto headset compensation, and Stereo Recording mode.

Feature

- System: Android 5.1.1 Lollipop

- Dual Processor: 2 GHz / Quad Core / 1.5 GHz / Quad Core / Qualcomm Snapdragon 810 (MSM8994) / GPU: Adreno 430

- Memory: Internal: 32 GB / RAM: 3 GB / Slot type: microSD / Max. slot capacity: 200 GB

- Display: 5.5" / TRILUMINOS™ Display with X-Reality / Resolution: 3840 x 2160 pixels / 806 ppi

- Camera: 23 Mpixels / Flash: Pulse LED / Front: 5 Mpixels / Video: 4K / Sony Exmor RS™ for mobile sensor

- Wireless: Bluetooth: 4.1 / DLNA, MHL, NFC / Wifi: 802.11 a/b/g/n/ac

- Connection: Jack 3.5 mm / micro USB

- Waterproof and dust tight (IP65 and IP68)

- Battery: 3430 mAh

- Weight: 181 grams

name: Sony Xperia Z5 Premium 4G E6883 Dual sim - Chrome Silver
description:
Xperia™ Z5 Premium features Sony’s latest large 1/2.3 Exmor RS™ for mobile 23 MP sensor and F2.0 G Lens, and Bionz for mobile designed in collaboration with Sony’s Alpha engineers for clear, vivid imagery every time.

The Xperia™ Z5 Premium is equipped with Hybrid Autofocus, which lets you capture action and movement accurately in various shooting conditions. Hybrid Autofocus uses two technologies to produce crisp and clear photos: Phase detection AF (PDAF) for faster shutter speed response and Contrast detection AF for added precision.

Imagine the best of Sony TV technologies delivered in a smartphone. A super-vivid and sharp display right in the palm of your hand. Meet Xperia™ Z5 Premium with a 4K Ultra HD display, this 5.5 inches smartphone packs in four times the resolution of Full HD for an unrivalled viewing experience.

Switch on extended standby to make battery standby time last longer. Your apps and functions will be turned off when you’re not using the display. However, you’ll still receive calls, texts, alarms and your choice of app notifications. Press the power button and everything is up and running again.

The Xperia™ Z5 Premium is designed for both functionality and durability. You can carry your device in the beach or during harsh weather and trust that it is protected from dust and moisture. The Xperia™ Z5 Premium’s power button has a new integrated fingerprint sensor. The button is intuitively placed on the side of the phone, so you’re able to pick up and securely unlock in a single movement.

name: Xiaomi Mi Note 3GB RAM/64GB Dual Sim- White Mobile White
description:
There's nothing quite as sleek and elegant as Mi Note. The moment it's in your hands, you'll realize how incredibly thin it is. The premium feel of glass against skin, curved at the edges for a better grip, is substantial. It is smooth to the touch, even along the sides where glass seamlessly tapers into aluminum. It's the most beautiful phone we've ever designed.

 

Mi Note was built to meet your ever increasing needs for power. It runs on a quad-core Qualcomm Snapdragon 801 2.5GHz processor and 3GB LPDDR3 RAM, which is a killer combination for multitasking, 3D games, HD movies, and running memory-intensive apps.

 

Go big with Mi Note's gorgeous 5.7" Sharp/JDI negative full HD display. It offers a contrast ratio of 1400:1 as opposed to 1000:1 on standard displays, producing even richer colors and contrasts for a spectacular visual experience. It also features the latest Sunlight Display, which uses hardware-level algorithms to adjust contrast for each pixel in real time, dramatically improving readability in sunlight. 

 

Great photos are taken anytime, anywhere. That's why the 13MP 2nd gen Sony IMX214 CMOS sensor comes with Optical Image Stabilization (OIS) to compensate for handheld movements, giving you sharp images even in low lighting. The 4MP front shooter brightens up smiles too, with large 2μm pixels to let more light in. It's 66% larger than the 1.2μm pixels found in average sensors and comes with Beautify, which intelligently applies one of 36 smart filters for amazing selfies.

 

Manage calls and messages on two separate SIM cards easily with 4G dual SIM, dual standby. Tailor preferred network and data settings for each card with intelligent dual SIM features, like creating custom SIM labels. Mi Note also automatically selects which SIM to use when you call or text someone based on history.

Feature

- 4G Dual SIM, fits micro and nano SIMs

- Sharp/JDI 2K QHD display 2560 x 1440 resolution at 515 PPI

- 1400:1 contrast ratio NEGA negative LCD technology

- Maximum readibility in sunlight

- Qualcomm® Snapdragon™ 801 quad-core 2.5GHz processor 3GB LPDDR3 RAM

- Adreno 330, renders 3D like a gaming console

- Large 3000mAh battery, Ultra-thin 6.95mm frame

name: Samsung Galaxy Tab A 10.1 Wi-Fi T580 (2016) - Black
description:
Enjoy powerful performance and a vibrant display with the black 10.1" Galaxy Tab A from Samsung. This tablet features a Samsung Exynos 7870 chipset, which utilizes an octa-core processor clocked at speeds up to 1.6 GHz. It comes with 2GB of RAM and 16GB of built-in storage. It's also equipped with a microSD slot that supports microSDXC cards up to 2TB. For high-speed Internet connectivity, 802.11a/b/g/n/ac Wi-Fi is built-in. Bluetooth 4.2 connectivity is also integrated for pairing with Bluetooth-enabled devices, such as select headphones and accessories.

This Samsung Galaxy Tab A houses a 10.1" capacitive touchscreen display with a WUXGA 1920 x 1080 screen resolution for viewing detailed high-definition content. The onboard front facing 2-megapixel and rear 8-megapixel cameras allow you take pictures of yourself and the world around you as well as making video calls over your Wi-Fi network.

A micro-USB 2.0 interface is available for mass storage connections and charging the device; a USB cable and charger are included. The internal 7300mAh battery is designed to offer hours of enjoyment before recharging is needed. The Galaxy Tab A comes with the Android 6.0 Marshmallow operating system, which delivers fluid and intuitive multi-touch navigation. The Tab A also supports multitasking tools, such as side-by-side application use.

The Tab A also supports multitasking tools, such as side-by-side application use.

name: Samsung Galaxy Tab A 7.0 WiFi T280 (2016) - Black
description:
The 7.0" Tab A 8GB Tablet from Samsung delivers powerful performance and wireless content sharing in a sleek, modern design. This tablet is powered by a quad-core 1.3 GHz Snapdragon 410 processor and has 1.5GB of RAM. It comes equipped with 8GB of built-in storage, a micro-USB port for data sharing, and a microSDXC card slot that supports up to 200GB of additional storage capacity. For high-speed Internet connectivity, Wi-Fi is built-in. Bluetooth 4.0 connectivity is also integrated for wireless pairing with compatible devices, such as headphones and other Bluetooth-enabled accessories.

This Galaxy Tab A houses a 7.0" IPS capacitive touchscreen display with a 1280 x 800 resolution for viewing all your favorite content. Additionally, the Tab A is equipped with a dual camera array: a front facing 2-megapixel camera and a rear-facing 5-megapixel camera. Photog-friendly features, such panoramic shots and the ability to create animated GIFs from a picture series, are also included. 

A micro-USB interface is built-in for mass storage connections and charging the device. The embedded 4000mAh battery is designed to offer hours of enjoyment before recharging is needed. The Galaxy Tab A comes with the Android 5.1.1 Lollipop operating system, which is designed for fluid and intuitive multi-touch navigation.
